<h1>Registeration</h1><br>
<p>Fill in the registeration form in order to get access to the Self-Moneytoring(tm) web app.</p>
<a href="/auth/login">If you have already registered to this site, please, go to the login page.</a><br>
<p id="otherwise">Otherwise go ahead, fill the god damn form already!</p>
<form action="/auth/register" method="post">
    <label for="email">Email</label>
    <input type="email" name="email" value="" id="email">
    <label for="password">Password</label>
    <input type="password" name="password" id="password">
    <label for="verificaton">Verify password</label>
    <input type="password" name="verification" id="verification">
    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
</form>
